        {
            "title": "地產｜京東傳斥2.8億購灣仔全幢酒店  或改作學生宿舍",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"地產｜京東傳斥2.8億購灣仔全幢酒店  或改作學生宿舍\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/49b0d0ce980e8683d284f9ba2e12c935cf1463332015d8c1421a6fba516afa28/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Ffortune_insight_694%2Fdbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">地產｜京東傳斥2.8億購灣仔全幢酒店  或改作學生宿舍</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據市場消息稱，灣仔軒尼詩道218號全幢酒店「218 Apartment」以約2.8億元售出，買家據悉為京東集團（09618），市場預料物業未來有機會改裝為學生宿舍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">資料顯示，該物業地盤面積約2,180方呎，總樓面約32,695方呎，現時作酒店用途，共設59間客房，房間面積約370至460方呎。若按成交價2.8億元計，呎價約8,564元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">酒店原屬商廈用途，內地企業首開集團於2007年以1.78億元購入，其後翻新並改裝為酒店。持貨約19年後轉售，帳面獲利約1.02億元，升值約57%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5e902b7c-5ade-3010-ba42-5b22b29a230a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">京東近月亦積極布局本港學生宿舍市場，早前已斥資7.5億元，向遠東發展（00035）購入油麻地上海街268號、原為海景絲麗酒店的全幢物業。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E4%BA%AC%E6%9D%B1%E5%82%B3%E6%96%A52-8%E5%84%84%E8%B3%BC%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%A2%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97-%E6%88%96%E6%94%B9%E4%BD%9C%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D-095019730.html",
